---
title: Crunchy Cod with Baked Wedges and Carrots
description: Tonight's dinner ... Crunchy cod! Not all kids like fish, but with these super crunchy top it's a dish everyone in the family can enjoy. Twist it up for the adults with some garlicky spinach to add some green to our version of fish and chips!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crunchy-cod-a4f6dcb6-c832c8de.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/crunchy-cod-5b17ff54ae08b5361f649c12-dd34bebb.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/crunchy-cod-5b17ff54ae08b5361f649c12
